summary: Simply changes the internal music of Breezehome with a quiet and relaxing (vanilla) tavern music :)
descriptionHtml:
This little mod was made by request for a special person ;)

Version:

1.0

Description:

Just changes the internal music of Breezehome with the classical vanilla tavern music (The same that can be heard in the taverns of Skyrim) (TavernB)

Installation:

Extract the content of the zip file in your data folder.

Uninstallation:

Delete "Breeze Music TBesp." from your data folder.

Compatabilities:

Not compatible with other mods which change Breezehome's music.

Contact:

Tvirus81
